snippet.title: DEATH NOTE Killer Within – Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Who has the Death Note?! 🍎
Uncover the truth as L or deceive to win as Kira when DEATH NOTE Killer Within launches on November 5, 2024. #DeathNoteKillerWithin
